And it is the most important paper in the history of the philosophy of language.

00:12.640 --> 00:17.360
It is very complicated, but I'm going to explain it now.

00:19.200 --> 00:24.160
Frege realizes that linguistic terms, words, have to have two levels of meaning.

00:24.160 --> 00:26.720
