00:33.520 --> 00:37.360
To illustrate this puzzle, I'm going to have you watch like a viral video.

00:56.720 --> 01:14.320
Okay, that was fun.

01:14.320 --> 01:18.320
The noteworthy thing about this interaction is that the woman, her name is Ellen,

01:19.120 --> 01:23.520
she already knows the meaning of the name Jay-Z.

01:23.520 --> 01:26.160
So it's not like what happens is that the guy tells her,

01:26.160 --> 01:30.400
oh, there's this name Jay-Z and the name refers to me.

01:30.400 --> 01:31.040
