03:55.840 --> 03:58.800
in the sense that the information that you get from sentence two

03:58.800 --> 04:02.240
can be, in some cases, not about language,

04:02.240 --> 04:03.920
not about the meanings of the words,

04:03.920 --> 04:06.160
but it can be something that has to be discovered

04:06.160 --> 04:08.640
through going out into the world and existing

04:08.720 --> 04:10.480
and discovering things like, namely,

04:10.480 --> 04:13.280
oh, this guy sitting next to me, he's a famous rapper.

04:13.280 --> 04:14.800
That's the point of this example.

04:14.800 --> 04:16.640
In the middle of the train ride,

04:16.640 --> 04:19.440
Ellen knows all the linguistic facts.

04:19.440 --> 04:23.040
